OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWarm for central and eastern
OL,6,Fareas with the Moray coast seasonally
OL,7,Fvery warm. Southeast winds fresh
OL,8,Faround coasts, pegging back
OL,9,Ftemperatures around the east coast.
OL,10,FStaying dry with sunny spells which
OL,11,Fturn hazy during the afternoon as
OL,12,Fhigher cloud increases.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloud thickening to bring
OL,15,Foccasional rain, this focused across
OL,16,FMoray and western Aberdeenshire, with
OL,17,Flittle expected to penetrate to the
OL,18,Feast coast. Southerly coastal winds
OL,19,Finitially fresh.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
