OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEastern coastal areas
OL,6,Fmilder than today. Elsewhere
OL,7,Fsignificantly cooler. Rather cloudy
OL,8,Fmorning with some patchy rain, mostly
OL,9,Fconfined across the far west. Mainly
OL,10,Fdry for the afternoon with brighter
OL,11,Fspells.
OL,12,
OL,13,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,14,Fearly Thursday, clearing to brighter
OL,15,Fspells and showers for the afternoon.
OL,16,FFriday turning wet and windy with best
OL,17,Fof shelter in east. Showers Saturday,
OL,18,Fmore frequent in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
